## Models

- **Primary:** {{PRIMARY_MODEL}} (e.g. Claude Opus 4.6)
- **Subagents:** Native Claude Code Agent tool (inherit parent model or override in agents/*.md)
- **Research:** {{RESEARCH_MODEL}} (e.g. Perplexity Sonar -- web search only, no code)

**Rules:**
- Subagents: ONLY native Claude Code Agent tool
- Maximum {{MAX_SUBAGENTS}} subagents simultaneously
- Heavy work -> subagents. Architecture and review -> main agent.

## Message Bus

| Operation | How |
|-----------|-----|
| My inbox | `{{INBOX_READ_CMD}}` |
| Send message | `{{MSG_SEND_CMD}}` |
| Update status | `{{STATUS_UPDATE_CMD}}` |

## Task Acceptance

1. Task unclear? -> ask clarifying questions
2. Task not mine? -> reject with reasoning, suggest who
3. Task clear? -> execute or delegate to subagent

Do NOT assume. Do NOT redirect without operator.

## Pipelines

| Pipeline | Steps |
|----------|-------|
| dev | plan -> code -> test -> review -> deploy |
| code | implement -> test -> commit |
| fix | reproduce -> fix -> test -> commit |
| review | read -> analyze -> comment -> approve/reject |
| research | search -> analyze -> propose |

## Cross-Review

- Cross-review on different models always
- Author != reviewer

